&lt;p&gt;Advert&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;We are looking for enthusiastic and committed Staff Nurses to come and join our dynamic team here on James Ward. &lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;We expect all our Nurses to be dedicated, hard working, self-motivated and keen to learn our specialities. We are seeking staff with the relevant post qualification experience but newly qualified staff are also welcome as there is a pathway to help you progress in your profession.&lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;We are proud to be one of the main Acute Medical Wards in Northwick Park Hospital, specialising mainly in Endocrine and Rheumatology. Looking after such specialities brings with it amazing professional challenges together with fantastic development opportunities. We pride ourselves on maintaining high standards of specialist care as well as creating a friendly work environment. &lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;We are a 34 bed unit dedicated to delivering the best nursing care to our patients, so take the opportunity now to come and join our team!&lt;/p&gt;
